## Additional Terms

### Commercial Use

Paqet UI is provided under the MIT license, which allows commercial use.
However:

1. You must comply with all dependent library licenses (see Third-Party Licenses above)
2. Some dependencies (like 3x-ui) have different licenses (GPL-3.0)
3. You must review licenses of all included dependencies
4. Commercial use must comply with all applicable licenses

### Distribution

If you distribute Paqet UI:

1. Include the full MIT license text
2. Include list of modifications (CHANGELOG.md)
3. Maintain copyright notices from original authors
4. Don't imply endorsement from original authors
5. Include all third-party licenses (see section above)

### Patents

No patent claims are made by this license. Users may need to obtain patent
licenses from third parties depending on their use case.

